k\to\infty
\to 1
\sin\frac{1}{\sqrt{k}}\approx\frac{1}{\sqrt{k}}
\frac{1}{\sqrt{k}}\sin^2\frac{1}{\sqrt{k}}\approx\frac{1}{k^{3/2}},
